Add a Report to a Dashboard from the Report
Go from report to dashboard with only a few clicks!

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions
To add a report to a dashboard: Create and Customize Dashboards
To add a report to a dynamic dashboard: Manage Dynamic Dashboards
On the Analytics tab, Reports tab, or report run page, select Add to Dashboard.
Choose whether to add the report to an existing dashboard or create a dashboard from the report. If necessary, name, describe, and choose a folder for the new dashboard.
Click Add.
Customize the dashboard widget.
Click Add.
Optionally, continue customizing the dashboard.
Click Save.
